  "body": "E. Klunko (ISTP), A. Volnova (SAI MSU), A. Pozanenko (IKI) report on\nbehalf of larger GRB follow-up collaboration:\n\nWe observed the field of the Swift GRB 100915A (Littlejohns et al.,\nGCN 11277) with AZT-33IK telescope of Sayan observatory (Mondy) on\nSep. 15 between (UT) 14:02 - 16:54 under variable weather conditions\nand mean seeing of about �~1.9\". In the two stacked images of two\nepochs we do not detect any source in enhanced XRT error circle\n(Osborne et al. GCN 11279). The upper limits (3 sigma) of the two\nstacked images based on USNO-B1.0 field stars are the following:\n\nt-t0,d � � �filter � �exp.,s �uplim\n0.53437 �R � � � 15*60 � 23.2\n0.60644 �R � � � 15*60 � 23.4"
